Definition: an occasion on which one is reminded of the nature of things in the real world
Example: this program is intended as a reality check for CEOs; after all those elaborate productions, I felt in need of a reality check
Synonyms: juncture, an, occasion, on, which, one, is, reminded, of, the, nature, things, in, real, world, this, program, intended, as, a, reality, check, for, CEOs, after, all, those, elaborate, productions, I, felt, need
Category: noun.event
